---
title: Beyond Meat® Burgers with Roasted Wedges and Zesty Cilantro Mayo
description: A caliente combo of Beyond Meat® and cilantro meet in this Mexican-inspired burger! Crispy potato wedges and a wholesome green salad make for satisfying sides.
